snippet.title: Penelope Cruz, Bella Hadid and Amber Heard dazzle on Cannes 'Pain and Glory' carpet
snippet.description:
Global stars including Deepika Padukone, Anja Rubik and Araya A. Hargate also wore striking outfits. (May 18)
